window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The <i>New York Times</i> best-selling Mortal Instruments continues - and so do the thrills and danger for Jace, Clary, and Simon. </p> <p>Can the lost be reclaimed? What price is too high to pay for love? Who can be trusted when sin and salvation collide? </p> <p>Darkness threatens to claim the Shadowhunters in the harrowing fifth book of the Mortal Instruments series.</p>"; 
